Limitation means that if the ministry buys under an auction, an extra tax will be imposed on gold parachutes, unless the failed head of the bank is retired.
By directly buying bad credits, the government will intervene aggressively to ensure that bosses' compensation is not exaggerated.
In addition to the above, existing gold parachute contracts will not be changed, the limitations relate only to new contracts to stimulate participation in the programme.
This is the first case in American history that will be in effect a legal limitation for the revenue of directors generals - said this measure by Democrat Barney Frank, chairman of the Congress committee, responsible for financial services.
The State will also have the right to acquire shares from the banks participating in the programme, thus reducing the risk of taxpayers, as they will ultimately be able to even gain profits with the transaction as soon as the economy is recovered and with it the bank.
